quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  53,33,Twalav win iwexxôen
  53,34,"i ifkan cwiî, iccuêen"
  53,35,"Day isâa tamusni n tbavnit, d$a iwala"
  53,36,Ne$ ur ippuxebbeô $ef tewôiqin n Musa
  53,37,Akked Ibôahim ineûêen
  53,38,Ur ipbibbi yiwen taâkkwemt n wayev
  53,39,"I umdan, siwa ayen inki"
  53,40,Ankay is a t iwali
  53,41,"Sinna, a t Ikafi s lufa"
  53,42,"Ih, ar Mass ik, taggara"
  53,43,"D Neppa i Issevûan, i Issruyen"
  53,44,"D Neppa i Ineqqen, i Issidiren"
  53,45,"D Neppa i Ixelqen tayuga, ddkeô akked nnta"
  53,46,Si tiqqit n l$ella ma tuzzel
  53,47,"FellaS, axlaq nniven"
  53,48,"D Neppa i I$ennun, i Iqenâan"
  53,49,D Neppa i d Mass n Ciâra
  53,50,D Neppa i Isnegren Âad imezwura
  53,51,"Si Tamud, ur d Iooi ara"
  53,52,"Agdud n Nuê, uqbel nnsen, war ccekk, iugar iten ddens, lbbwe$v"
  53,53,Issenger tid inneqlaben
  53,54,Idel iten s wayen idellen
  53,55,Anta talalt n Mass ik ara tnamerev
  53,56,Wagi d aneddaô seg ineddaôen n zik
  53,57,A d taéé tin d ippaééen
  53,58,"War Öebbi, ur illi ara p id issdehôen"
  53,59,Iswehm ikwen wawal a
  53,60,La tdessem ur la tepprum
  53,61,Kunwi di zzhu
  53,62,"Knut i Öebbi, âabdet"